<span id="freeTextContainer15207859115841498017">The last couple of pages of this book made me chuckle. It&apos;s not everyday that you read a book about a cosmetician for the dead, an embalmer, and a pet cemetery employee with a poetic bent. The Hollywood Forever cemetery holds new meaning for me now. </span>
  <span id="freeText15207859115841498017" style="display:none">The last couple of pages of this book made me chuckle. It's not everyday that you read a book about a cosmetician for the dead, an embalmer, and a pet cemetery employee with a poetic bent. The Hollywood Forever cemetery holds new meaning for me now. </span>
